type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Lola is buying "},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_emphasis_non-ital","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"seeds"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for her garden. What will they grow  into? "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_hilight_teacher_inst_new","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Revisit "},{"type":"element","name":"rac_highlight_teacher_inst_Italic","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"seed"}]},{"type":"text","text":" Vocabulary Card. "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_d-hed_page_number","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"pages 8–9 "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"It looks like Lola planted two rows of seeds. How can we separate the two rows into two equal groups?  "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_d-hed_page_number","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"pages 14–15 "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"What is happening? What are green shoots? "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_d-hed_page_number","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"page 24 "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Lola hung silver bells in her garden, just like in the poem! How many bells do you see on this page? How many bells will be in each group if we separate the six bells into two equal groups? "}]}]},{"type":"element","name":"section","elements":[{"type":"element","name":"rac_column_heds_with_rule","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Talk About It "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Let’s talk about the guiding question: What is one thing Lola puts in her garden? "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_body-text","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Use Equity Sticks to ask several children to share their responses. "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_body-text","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Possible response